<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PS HUB</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://img.edvido.com/unnamed_png-3aca4.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="Project.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header id="home">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://wallpaper.dog/large/972741.jpg">
            <h1>PS HUB</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="header-buttons">
            <% if (currentUser) { %>
                <span class="header-btn">Hi, <%= currentUser.name %> (<%= currentUser.role %>)</span>
                <% if (currentUser.role === "user") { %>
                    <a href="/my-orders" class="header-btn text-decoration-none">My Orders</a>
                <% } %>
                <% if (currentUser.role === "admin") { %>
                    <a href="/admin/orders" class="header-btn text-decoration-none">Manage Orders</a>
                <% } %>
                <a href="/logout" class="header-btn text-decoration-none">Logout</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/login" class="header-btn text-decoration-none">Login</a>
                <a href="/register" class="header-btn text-decoration-none">Register</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#products">Products</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section class="products-list" id="products">
            <h1>Games</h1>

            <!-- Only admins can add a new game -->
            <% if (currentUser && currentUser.role === "admin") { %>
                <form method="POST" action="/add" class="row g-2 justify-content-center mb-4 px-3">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
                        <input type="text" name="name" class="form-control" placeholder="Game name" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-8 col-md-2">
                        <input type="number" name="price" class="form-control" placeholder="Price (₹)" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
                        <input type="text" name="image" class="form-control" placeholder="Image URL (optional)">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-4 col-md-2">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Add Game</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            <% } %>

            <div class="product-container">
                <% games.forEach(function(game) { %>
                    <div class="product-card">
                        <img src="<%= game.image %>" alt="<%= game.name %>">
                        <h3><%= game.name %></h3>
                        <p>&#8377; <%= game.price %>.00</p>

                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2 mt-2">
                            <% if (currentUser && currentUser.role === "admin") { %>
                                <a href="/edit/<%= game.id %>" class="btn btn-sm btn-warning">Edit</a>
                                <form method="POST" action="/delete/<%= game.id %>" onsubmit="return confirm('Delete this game?');">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-danger">Delete</button>
                                </form>
                            <% } else if (currentUser && currentUser.role === "user") { %>
                                <a href="/buy/<%= game.id %>" class="btn btn-sm btn-success">Buy</a>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-sm btn-success">Login to Buy</a>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section" id="about">
            <h2>About US</h2>
            <p>

Welcome to PS HUB, your trusted destination for all things PlayStation.

At PS HUB, we specialize in providing authentic PlayStation consoles, controllers, games, and gaming accessories to gamers who demand quality and reliability. Whether you're upgrading your setup, looking for the latest game releases, or replacing a controller, we offer a carefully selected range of products to meet your gaming needs.

Our goal is simple: to deliver genuine products, competitive pricing, and exceptional customer service. We are committed to creating a seamless shopping experience with secure transactions, fast order processing, and dedicated support every step of the way.

As passionate members of the gaming community, we understand what gamers expect. That's why we continuously strive to bring the best PlayStation products and accessories to our customers while maintaining the highest standards of quality and service.

Thank you for choosing PS HUB. We look forward to helping you take your gaming experience to the next level.

PS HUB — Your Ultimate PlayStation Destination.
</p>
        </section>

        <section class="contact-section" id="contact">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <form class="contact-form">
                <label for="name">Name</label>
                <input type="text">

                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input type="email">

                <label for="message">Message</label>
                <textarea name="" rows="4"></textarea>

                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>PS HUB &copy; June 2026. All Rights Reserved</p>
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="#home">Home</a>
            <a href="#products">Products</a>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </div>

        <p>Follow Us on:</p>

        <div class="social-media">
            <a href="https://facebook.com/playstation"><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i></a>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/playstation"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></a>
            <a href="https://youtube.com/playstation"><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i></a>
            <a href="https://x.com/playstation"><i class="fa-brands fa-x-twitter"></i></a>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
